1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with the automated assessment of image quality in the context of diabetic retinopathy using deep learning, which is a core area of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses a deep learning framework for the automated assessment of image quality, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes an AI-based method for the automated assessment of image quality in the context of diabetic retinopathy. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with the retrieval of information from color fundus images in the context of diabetic retinopathy screening. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the analysis of color fundus images, which is a form of multimedia data.
